	unsigned.
	(iocs_trap): Fix stack frames for IOCS call handlers.

	* libvx68kgtk/gtkconsole.cc (handle_expose_event): Test the expose
	area to avoid drawing outside of the screen area.

	* doc/vx68k.texi (Human68k): Updated.

